cs.RO, cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a grasping system that utilizes a 3D reconstruction to enable geometric awareness in robots. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is also likely as the paper involves using partial views of objects to generate 3D reconstructions. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another likely category as the paper utilizes deep learning techniques to learn the 3D reconstruction and grasp success classifier. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper involves developing an intelligent grasping system that can reason about the full 3D geometry of objects. 
- cs.GR (Graphics) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper involves generating 3D reconstructions of objects.
